Developers team, I would say

00:18:18.910 --> 00:18:22.720
that we really didn't run into
anything that was kind of an,

00:18:22.720 --> 00:18:24.025
oh, that's really weird.

00:18:24.025 --> 00:18:26.560
But it's more like, hmm, OK,
I'll read the documentation,

00:18:26.560 --> 00:18:28.810
which is actually what Google
really shines on in my opinion

00:18:28.810 --> 00:18:31.060
is the documentation
is exemplary.

00:18:31.060 --> 00:18:32.550
So we had actually
a very easy time

00:18:32.550 --> 00:18:35.310
implementing the YouTube API.

00:18:35.310 --> 00:18:36.030
JAREK WILKIEWICZ: Good
